# 🏥 Enterprise Health Platform Modernization  
### 📊 End-to-End Healthcare Data Engineering & Analytics (MySQL)

---

## 📌 Overview  
This project simulates a real-world **enterprise healthcare data modernization system**, transforming a legacy database into a **scalable, normalized, and analytics-ready platform**.

The system is designed to improve **data quality, reporting performance, and operational efficiency** while enabling advanced analytics for healthcare workflows.

---

## 🎯 Business Problem  
Legacy healthcare systems often face:

- Data duplication and redundancy  
- Poor query performance  
- Inconsistent patient and claims records  
- Limited analytics and reporting capabilities  

---

## 🚀 Solution  
This project addresses these challenges by:

- Designing a **normalized relational database (3NF)**  
- Cleaning and standardizing legacy datasets  
- Migrating data into structured schema  
- Building analytical queries and reporting views  
- Optimizing performance using indexing techniques  

